{"tid":1534222,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母 你地成班係新聞組定行動組呀","createTime":"2019-09-03T02:46:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T03:07:57.000Z","uid":58008,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c661c6438bc2b883b8d8e3420ee67dc0ebdca05d","tid":1534222,"uid":58008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:46:16.000Z","msg":"去到依個階段仲係到整合新聞<br />\n係呀 佢地周街打人打撚死人咁又點呀？<br />\n淨撚係識係到打飛機睇新聞睇記者會<br />\n屌你老母 知你好撚嬲啦 得啦得啦好撚叻<br />\n睇下前線心聲 幾撚灰<br />\n你班仆街日撚日呀Q勝利法<br />\n心理上麻包袋 廢話一堆 dllm<br />\n做唔撚到就咪撚講啦廢閪"},{"pid":"401fd3c548c89f465cb8c91c651bdc2c4f05b09f","tid":1534222,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:46:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我唔想知佢錄音內容<br />\n我推到同溫層既大家知道<br />\n你地負責幫手去fb啊等等宣傳得唔得<br />\n唔好再理膠post喇 關注返行動post<br />\n再好好運用6月至今每個核彈去twitter做文宣喇<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/twitter4HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwitter4HK&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFFuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=0d1fc816\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/twitter4HK</a><br />\n<br />\n[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，<br />\n請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n901 機場測試係成功<br />\n辛苦曬行左20公里既手足 勿被帶風向<br />\n<br />\n908 我希望美國巴絲手足都有遊行<br />\n聲援香港同埋同要請求美國國會通過人權法!<br />\n<br />\n908 建議：<br />\n-大量英文文宣/紙牌<br />\n-高舉大量美國議員大頭相<br />\n-高舉大量國旗<br />\n-唔建議勇武，因為主題涉及美國<br />\n(另一原因係 廢時佢又區區有狗搜身兼 補充文具需時又珍貴)<br />\n-領事館門前唱國歌<br />\n<br />\n無人申請不反 都要照上街<br />\n需要文宣制圖 然後我幫你宣傳<br />\n由今日開始宣! 908照上街!<br />\n<br />\n建議內容copy某位巴打既<br />\n9月我要照上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"e05f88f6e82b781700fd7570bc7d9cef81c3a41b","tid":1534222,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:46:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月8！到時見！</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"95ad927d9bf967c884106ffdb4d213bd100960d9","tid":1534222,"uid":293698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:46:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"89aa68a0679cf480b3a6bfc230ed5a0564de760e","tid":1534222,"uid":310535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:48:09.000Z","msg":"整理一直以來發生過咩事係必須嫁woo, 屌咩？"},{"pid":"582162ddece7a4d7fb8b6ea5c4573970e322f061","tid":1534222,"uid":58008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89aa68a0679cf480b3a6bfc230ed5a0564de760e","tid":1534222,"uid":310535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:48:09.000Z","msg":"整理一直以來發生過咩事係必須嫁woo, 屌咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:51:01.000Z","msg":"繼續整理<br />\n人地繼續做 你keep住整理就得<br />\n寫到本書出黎 革命就成功 加油"},{"pid":"868fb7baf59f7e106268a545100c115ea3fd8fb7","tid":1534222,"uid":310535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"582162ddece7a4d7fb8b6ea5c4573970e322f061","tid":1534222,"uid":58008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89aa68a0679cf480b3a6bfc230ed5a0564de760e","tid":1534222,"uid":310535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:48:09.000Z","msg":"整理一直以來發生過咩事係必須嫁woo, 屌咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:51:01.000Z","msg":"繼續整理<br />\n人地繼續做 你keep住整理就得<br />\n寫到本書出黎 革命就成功 加油"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:57:56.000Z","msg":"Why not both? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾時成功過？"},{"pid":"c9136c4a2b7ceecbcd5fe856e9d0ea3358777fe4","tid":1534222,"uid":58008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"868fb7baf59f7e106268a545100c115ea3fd8fb7","tid":1534222,"uid":310535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"582162ddece7a4d7fb8b6ea5c4573970e322f061","tid":1534222,"uid":58008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89aa68a0679cf480b3a6bfc230ed5a0564de760e","tid":1534222,"uid":310535,"lik